  "2387470": {
    "name": "神秘的电梯先生 / MR.ELEVATOR",
    "steam_appid": 2387470,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;BitSummit 2024 Sponsor Award PlayStation®PRIZE, INNOVATIVE OUTLAW AWARD NOMINEE&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款冒险解谜游戏，五位主角（男女）乘坐上神秘的“电梯先生”，在迷失的异世界中为寻求各自所求之物而解开谜团。您将自由探索这个仿佛用早期Windows画图软件绘制的独特世界，沉浸式享受面前出现的谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/f37e95ebd254cde03704e54fcb1b2e85.poster.avif?t=1771475590\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/f37e95ebd254cde03704e54fcb1b2e85.webm?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/f37e95ebd254cde03704e54fcb1b2e85.mp4?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我是电梯先生。<br>你在找什么吗？如果你遇到了麻烦，我或许能帮上忙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/e236773cabbfd75b609d73e7157839cd.poster.avif?t=1771475590\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/e236773cabbfd75b609d73e7157839cd.webm?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/e236773cabbfd75b609d73e7157839cd.mp4?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看来有五名男女迷失在这里了。<br>你是……在找什么人吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/b33a719f78c51f3781da2fa4ee84e090.poster.avif?t=1771475590\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/b33a719f78c51f3781da2fa4ee84e090.webm?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里排着好多门啊。我们来试试敲一敲或敲打一下它们。<br>哎呀，门打开了呢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/f024574f4d44d76d18b6347197ec62ef.poster.avif?t=1771475590\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/f024574f4d44d76d18b6347197ec62ef.webm?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/f024574f4d44d76d18b6347197ec62ef.mp4?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时你可能会在黑暗中行走，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/0d66a59fadc5b6f2d25d2a38762ca92f.poster.avif?t=1771475590\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/0d66a59fadc5b6f2d25d2a38762ca92f.webm?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/0d66a59fadc5b6f2d25d2a38762ca92f.mp4?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在广阔的原野中，你或许会遇到奇特的生物或是石像。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/5431e7b35b5312646861be9eb2dbbef6.poster.avif?t=1771475590\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/5431e7b35b5312646861be9eb2dbbef6.webm?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/5431e7b35b5312646861be9eb2dbbef6.mp4?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个坏掉的智能手机还有用处吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/aaca21304299be41dfb7de7f4e026f38.poster.avif?t=1771475590\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/aaca21304299be41dfb7de7f4e026f38.webm?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/aaca21304299be41dfb7de7f4e026f38.mp4?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个看起来很适合拧螺丝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/73a7aeae204af33d45a81b4d955923c6.poster.avif?t=1771475590\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/73a7aeae204af33d45a81b4d955923c6.webm?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/73a7aeae204af33d45a81b4d955923c6.mp4?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时你可能会拿着一本书，思考如何使用找到的物品，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/507afadcf9bc4cb2a84c2ddbb6131c95.poster.avif?t=1771475590\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/507afadcf9bc4cb2a84c2ddbb6131c95.webm?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/507afadcf9bc4cb2a84c2ddbb6131c95.mp4?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可能会倾听对讲机传来的声音。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/e4ff0316dd2b0e0fc0f18a42738a4dee.poster.avif?t=1771475590\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/e4ff0316dd2b0e0fc0f18a42738a4dee.webm?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387470/extras/e4ff0316dd2b0e0fc0f18a42738a4dee.mp4?t=1771475590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怎么样？你找到你要找的东西了吗？<br>如果你愿意，可以慢慢地寻找你的目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我会一直守护着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■操作方法（按 Esc 显示）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >移动：W、A、S、D<br>视角：移动鼠标<br>跑步：Shift<br><br>伸出右手：鼠标右键<br>伸出左手：鼠标左键<br>移动光标：按住鼠标任意键的同时移动鼠标<br><br>动作（将光标对准可执行动作的对象时）：<br>　右手：3、4、C、V<br>　左手：1、2、Z、X<br><br>切换道具<br>　右手：E<br>　左手：Q<br><br>放大道具（持有道具时）：<br>　双手：长按两个鼠标键<br><br>切换光标（伸出手时）：Shift</p>",
